         <abstract id="aspace_a84c72403fe3cb9d364fe1f949cf0fb6">The records consist of correspondence, policies, statements, accident and injury reports, certificates of insurance, payment statements, and printed materials documenting the activities and operations of the Yale Insurance Office.</abstract>
